    "科学管理 · 贴心提醒 · 健康成长\n\nPawRoutine 帮助您记录宠物的日常活动、健康状况和成长轨迹，让每一只毛孩子都得到最科学的照顾。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Smart Management · Caring Reminders · Healthy Growth\n\nPawRoutine helps you record your pet's daily activities, health status, and growth trajectory, ensuring every furry friend gets the most scientific care."
          }
        },
        "zh" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "科学管理 · 贴心提醒 · 健康成长\n\nPawRoutine 帮助您记录宠物的日常活动、健康状况和成长轨迹，让每一只毛孩子都得到最科学的照顾。"
