    "请确保在系统设置中允许 FurryNote 发送通知。同时检查「设置 → 提醒默认值」中对应的提醒开关是否已开启。添加新宠物后，系统会自动根据当前提醒设置为该宠物注册通知。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Make sure you have allowed FurryNote to send notifications in system settings. Also check that the corresponding reminder switch is turned on in Settings → Default Reminders. After adding a new pet, the system will automatically register notifications based on your current reminder settings."
          }
        },
        "zh" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "请确保在系统设置中允许 FurryNote 发送通知。同时检查「设置 → 提醒默认值」中对应的提醒开关是否已开启。添加新宠物后，系统会自动根据当前提醒设置为该宠物注册通知。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "请确保在系统设置中允许 PawRoutine 发送通知。同时检查「设置 → 提醒默认值」中对应的提醒开关是否已开启。添加新宠物后，系统会自动根据当前提醒设置为该宠物注册通知。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Make sure system settings allow PawRoutine to send notifications. Also check that the corresponding reminder switch is on in \"Settings → Reminder Defaults\". After adding a new pet, the system will automatically register notifications based on current reminder settings."
          }
        },
        "zh" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "请确保在系统设置中允许 PawRoutine 发送通知。同时检查「设置 → 提醒默认值」中对应的提醒开关是否已开启。添加新宠物后，系统会自动根据当前提醒设置为该宠物注册通知。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
